description: Alexis Ziritt is the co-founder of the t-shirt company Fistful Apparel and the indie comics co-op Calavera Comics. Alexis is originally from Venezuela but has lived in Tampa for the past decade. He's been published in Complex Magazine and Heavy Metal, among others. His kung fu is strong.
name: Alexis Ziritt
